INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('12', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p>要说最无聊的事，学生时代莫过于上课。每次只要语文老师开始讲文言文，数学老师开始讲函数，英语老师开始讲阅读……蛋黄就觉得只要不听讲，其他无论干什么都是一件有趣的活动<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880384-kc57i7wptcsf65hlea0lx6-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880384-kc57i7wptcsf65hlea0lx6-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>但是有时候干别的事太明显也会被老师抓，那么想选择一个既有趣又不容易被抓的活动那当然就是“对课本进行二次创作”，无论是插图也好，函数关系式也好……只要有脑洞分分钟就能化腐朽为神奇。所以今天和大家分享的就是那些被玩坏了的课本涂鸦们<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880392-s69lhytor9acle6rydv7rw-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880392-s69lhytor9acle6rydv7rw-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>说到课本涂鸦，最忙的大概就是“诗圣”杜甫了<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880397-gq9ucl7wla6m5u6xsou165-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880397-gq9ucl7wla6m5u6xsou165-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>从送水工到美国队长<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880401-qimtgxpdbrrh8dar2fkc57-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880401-qimtgxpdbrrh8dar2fkc57-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"><br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880404-2ktqotl3pcc0hrxe3ato67-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880404-2ktqotl3pcc0hrxe3ato67-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>从忙着自拍到忙着把妹，诸多繁忙事物加深怪不得他要感叹“艰难苦恨繁霜鬓，潦倒新停浊酒杯。”</p>\r\n<p>眼看杜甫人气一路高涨，关汉卿骑着摩托车决定开始他的表演<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880411-6o3d1gsxmbbndte9tgl9tj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880411-6o3d1gsxmbbndte9tgl9tj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>孟子说“你有摩托车了不起？让开我的更环保！”<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880417-9he3ag9wlrkxfequtvpyq3-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880417-9he3ag9wlrkxfequtvpyq3-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>课本入选率最高的鲁迅先生更是呵呵一笑“我不是鄙视谁，我只是说在座的都是垃圾。”<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880421-socho3t9adpmasndps78nj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880421-socho3t9adpmasndps78nj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>你以为就这些名人被玩坏了吗？太天真了，只要有插图分分钟创作给你看<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880426-0hdniwzl94hlqq1rae06l1-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880426-0hdniwzl94hlqq1rae06l1-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>肥宅——曹丕<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880432-oo3m62r6a1fczshau3oz4v-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880432-oo3m62r6a1fczshau3oz4v-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>李商隐：我的渔网袜，时尚最时尚<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880436-eyeuxtqib8nu4s50utqjzb-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880436-eyeuxtqib8nu4s50utqjzb-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>被通缉的海贼乔巴——刘基<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880440-4s6ncov1vsuad72mxpcdh1-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880440-4s6ncov1vsuad72mxpcdh1-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>苏轼：便秘怎么办，在线等，挺急的<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880445-b2e1pqpzloa8s5d0j965t8-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880445-b2e1pqpzloa8s5d0j965t8-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>偶尔也要来一发</p>\r\n<p>你们别说，课本涂鸦还真不是我大天朝的专利，从战斗民族到脑洞清奇的日本，全世界的学生都掌握这一项名叫“课本涂鸦的神技”。</p>\r\n<p>我们先来看看战斗民族的课本涂鸦<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880449-yka8o9vrgz93hbhzuuf5sv-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880449-yka8o9vrgz93hbhzuuf5sv-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>课本没打码，放着我来<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880452-kcns7unkgmksi33cygwg6l-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880452-kcns7unkgmksi33cygwg6l-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>拿破仑也逃脱不了<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880456-wkwyxbif1c9zxfcg7eq2zx-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880456-wkwyxbif1c9zxfcg7eq2zx-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>各位我先吐为敬</p>\r\n<p>棒子坐不住了，他们说“课本涂鸦也是我们国家发明的啊！放着我要去申遗！”<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880460-im78tdg7pcsne1u6kylow7-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880460-im78tdg7pcsne1u6kylow7-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>微博话题#上学像所整容院#的现实版<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880464-zdxvu6idr6ix0mwteynxul-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880464-zdxvu6idr6ix0mwteynxul-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>棒子国的男团是如何诞生的<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880470-r6uuftohqyur0voz9aizkj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880470-r6uuftohqyur0voz9aizkj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>整容实例分享</p>\r\n<p>而岛国的孩子们，则是完美继承哼了画漫画的天赋，哪怕一个数学公式都可以创作<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880474-o8foornsdo2y1vxt0c71l3-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880474-o8foornsdo2y1vxt0c71l3-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>歪？妖妖灵吗我的数学课本上有个hentai！<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880477-co4tg44cw9zcndotgj4n6e-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880477-co4tg44cw9zcndotgj4n6e-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>萌妹子给你看胖次哟<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880482-zvn1478p0hamd5g29ic2sj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880482-zvn1478p0hamd5g29ic2sj-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>花名册上的皮卡丘与蓝胖子，那天所有人都回忆起了，被皮卡丘与蓝胖子支配的恐惧<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880485-n7e5i3rqzyyty28h6vvr83-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880485-n7e5i3rqzyyty28h6vvr83-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n<p>就算戴的是化学式改成的眼镜，我想大雄的成绩也不会有起色吧。</p>\r\n<p>今天蛋黄一边搬砖，一边在想我当年同桌的画的插图，真是一个灵魂画手啊，可惜不给带手机去学校没有留下来做纪念 。不知不觉老阿姨·蛋黄的学生时代已经过去了那么多年，真是让人唏嘘。</p>\r\n<p>看这篇文还在上学的小阔爱们，请记住一句话“不在课本上涂鸦的学生时代是不完整的！”所以<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880488-6acyo31o444ubmtiyj96a6-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510904880488-6acyo31o444ubmtiyj96a6-3aa9a1ad9b2df641de9960f4f66d536c\"></p>\r\n\n            \n          </div>');
INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('13', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p>▼菜市场上，计较那么多干嘛？<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510834883828-inq6mu5z0sijupwappc4n0-261434bc86c6d07ebaabf68dad77ab18!560\" class=\"shared-image\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"1518\" width=\"230\" height=\"759\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510834883828-inq6mu5z0sijupwappc4n0-261434bc86c6d07ebaabf68dad77ab18!560\"></p>\r\n<p>▼心里的痛楚，不能说出来<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510834883825-t2lhtxfm2zstwd2xsraine-261434bc86c6d07ebaabf68dad77ab18!560\" class=\"shared-image\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"1481\" width=\"230\" height=\"740\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510834883825-t2lhtxfm2zstwd2xsraine-261434bc86c6d07ebaabf68dad77ab18!560\"></p>\r\n<p>▼身为老爸，要以身作则<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510834883818-dos741n9zqoufpmp2vpso8-261434bc86c6d07ebaabf68dad77ab18!560\" class=\"shared-image\" data-width=\"460\" data-height=\"1518\" width=\"230\" height=\"759\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510834883818-dos741n9zqoufpmp2vpso8-261434bc86c6d07ebaabf68dad77ab18!560\"></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n\n            \n          </div>');
INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('14', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p>小编香菜是一个泪腺十分发达的人，每当看到影视剧中那些动人的情节都会止不住泪流满面。</p>\r\n<p>有人说这是脆弱，也有人说这是矫情。Anyway，只是遇到太过催泪的影视剧的时候，我相信大多数的人都是会哭的<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556692-vs0bxvzrtti19xmk6nbx1b-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556692-vs0bxvzrtti19xmk6nbx1b-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>最近，日本网站goo就针对这些催泪的影视剧做了一项调查：票选10部最催泪的日本电影。</p>\r\n<p>接下来让我们看一下都有哪些电影上榜吧！</p>\r\n<p>▼第10位《如父如子》</p>\r\n<p>这部提名第66届戛纳电影节主竞赛单元的影片由日本著名演员歌手福山雅治主演。</p>\r\n<p>讲述了两个结婚多年且生活幸福的夫妻在多年后发现自己的儿子并非亲生，而是意外抱错，</p>\r\n<p>朝夕相处的父子情遇上血浓于水的父子情该如何做出选择？<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556720-wd3mposl6lybod02u7hwn3-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556720-wd3mposl6lybod02u7hwn3-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>生活中，我们总是在寻找答案，可是下意识的举动不会骗人，当你在睡梦中喊着那个人的名字的时候，一切也就有了答案。</p>\r\n<p>▼第9位《入殓师》</p>\r\n<p>第32届加拿大蒙特利尔国际电影节最高大奖。</p>\r\n<p>第81届奥斯卡金像奖最佳外语片奖。</p>\r\n<p>第29届香港电影金像奖最佳亚洲电影奖。</p>\r\n<p>这些傲人的成绩摆在这就证明了它的好。</p>\r\n<p>一部以一名入殓师新手的视角，去观察各种各样的死亡，凝视围绕在逝者周围的充满爱意的人们的作品<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556729-uiib9umwimhlqcuhdm6kig-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556729-uiib9umwimhlqcuhdm6kig-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第8位《太阳之歌》</p>\r\n<p>与《在世界的中心呼唤爱》，《现在，很想见你》一起被称为“纯爱三部曲”。</p>\r\n<p>讲述了居住在海滨小镇的16岁女孩雨音薰因为患有XP色素性干皮症，不能接受阳光照射，无法像其他人一样在阳光下自由玩耍。</p>\r\n<p>在深夜踱步时渐渐喜欢上了经常路过车站的男孩藤代孝治，她想要告白，但对于生命脆弱的她来说一切都显得很奢侈<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556737-yyg5dcb46rrx3nven18bhi-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556737-yyg5dcb46rrx3nven18bhi-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第7位《第八日的蝉》</p>\r\n<p>如果我努力活着，上帝一定不会嫌弃我吧？</p>\r\n<p>小池荣子姐姐获得最佳女配角的一部伦理之作。</p>\r\n<p>讲述了因为一段不论之恋，造成了两代人的人生悲剧的故事<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556745-ha3dlvukwnnf6mimqste83-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556745-ha3dlvukwnnf6mimqste83-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第六位《海猿》</p>\r\n<p>一群热血的海上保安人员，一次次勇敢的奔赴救援现场，为了营救他人不惜牺牲生命。</p>\r\n<p>这种歌颂警察，消防员的电影并不少见，也正是因为这些电影，让我们了解了这样一群默默奉献的人<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556752-sga2fvv8l3cpnd6ea2lpp8-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556752-sga2fvv8l3cpnd6ea2lpp8-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第五位《永远的0》</p>\r\n<p>影帝冈田准一之作。</p>\r\n<p>讲述了有志青年佐伯健太郎对祖父生前战友进行探访追忆，以及探寻战死的祖父宫部久藏的过去的经历的故事。</p>\r\n<p>这部电影在第38届日本电影学院奖中荣获包括最佳影片在内的八项大奖<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556761-dvv5fmudtviitwh9mo1ajg-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556761-dvv5fmudtviitwh9mo1ajg-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第四位《总是守候幸福的三丁目》</p>\r\n<p>第29届日本电影学院最佳影片。</p>\r\n<p>一部温情励志电影，平凡的生活，对生活抱有的希望与信念，是我们在这个忙碌的社会里最想拥有的<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556771-7eg065iaf18dbbmcvqztdz-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556771-7eg065iaf18dbbmcvqztdz-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第三位《生命最后一个月的花嫁》</p>\r\n<p>影片根据真实故事改编。</p>\r\n<p>讲述了与乳癌进行坚强斗争的24岁少女长岛千惠，在她生命只剩下最后一个月的时候，为了实现穿上婚纱的梦想，与男友携手步入婚礼殿堂，但在婚后不久终因病情恶化，悄然离世的悲剧爱情片<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556780-htlxgpqzpdi0uqbhbob5wf-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556780-htlxgpqzpdi0uqbhbob5wf-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第二位《现在，很想见你》</p>\r\n<p>纯爱三部曲中的第二部。</p>\r\n<p>也是当年把中村狮童和竹内结子牵在一起的经典作品，后来也有改编成日剧版播出。</p>\r\n<p>直到现在每当听到由ORANGE RANGE演唱的主题曲 「花」，影视中的画面还是会浮现在眼前<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556791-io7boco7ua59gp0frh51uv-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556791-io7boco7ua59gp0frh51uv-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>▼第一位《在世界的中心呼唤爱》</p>\r\n<p>总是被提起，也被翻拍的经典之作。</p>\r\n<p>大概不了解日影的人也听过这部电影。</p>\r\n<p>看来无论是10年前还是10年后，这部造成社会现象的大热卖电影在大家的心里都是无法替代的催泪之作<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556805-dw84wuzal0sopigrmpdrat-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510927556805-dw84wuzal0sopigrmpdrat-58e9353864a7c1dc617793d482ae1e98\"></p>\r\n<p>以上就是日本网友评选的经典催泪电影，不知道你心目中最催泪的电影是哪一部呢？ </p>\r\n\n            \n          </div>');
INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('15', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p>婚后淡出了大众视野颇久的星女郎张雨绮，今天突然冲上了热搜第一，鸡哥定睛一看，哇塞，女神竟然生了一对龙凤胎，一把凑成了个“好”字，两个宝宝的满月照也首次曝光，十分得可爱，真是恭喜女神<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422382-ap54cxnirol7za4v08d1vi-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422382-ap54cxnirol7za4v08d1vi-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>张雨绮的宝宝长这样，完全继承了妈妈的美貌基因，超级可爱有没有！<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422391-id6si1pgaehusov76fbgo9-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422391-id6si1pgaehusov76fbgo9-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>网友纷纷送上祝福的同时也表示十分羡慕，能生龙凤胎也是厉害了<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422395-qb8s8lrybchk4bh3ntpaw3-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422395-qb8s8lrybchk4bh3ntpaw3-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>说起张雨绮，大家对她应该会有如下的印象吧~</p>\r\n<p><span>混杂在张馨予、张歆艺、张予曦等人中傻傻分不清的“名盲”大军中的一员<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422397-oo9vkcn3t8yeszs2fb4pqt-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422397-oo9vkcn3t8yeszs2fb4pqt-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></span></p>\r\n<p><span>哎嘛，求放过，连连看太伤眼，鸡哥选择认输<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422400-825f8wie7kwb8x7dl10guk-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422400-825f8wie7kwb8x7dl10guk-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"><br></span></p>\r\n<p><span>王全安前妻</span></p>\r\n<p>张雨绮因电影“白鹿原”结识了导演王全安，两人在电影拍摄期间，曾被曝出深夜密会的绯闻。2011年4月5日，媒体曝出张雨绮和王全安订婚的消息，17日媒体曝光了两人甜蜜外出的照片，18日张雨绮与大自己20岁的王全安在西安领取结婚证宣布结婚<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422407-5ivytcowlsd3dsgg736cnn-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422407-5ivytcowlsd3dsgg736cnn-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>好景不长，2014年9月发生了一件震惊娱乐圈的事情：张雨绮老公王全安因涉嫌嫖娼被抓。不过，张雨绮也大气回应此事：“我们俩会坦白面对，共同承担。”但好景不长，2015年7月2日，张雨绮发文宣布与王全安离婚<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422409-f3lpb524uxzukuwc9c3tr5-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422409-f3lpb524uxzukuwc9c3tr5-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>许多人都不能理解，家有娇妻张雨绮，王全安为什么还要去嫖娼？<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422411-19m3l11sppwrjgc9ih0d0o-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422411-19m3l11sppwrjgc9ih0d0o-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>霸道女总裁</p>\r\n<p>2016年2月8日，周星驰的电影“美人鱼”上映，饰演美人鱼的林允开始出现在大众的视野中，而饰演霸道富家女的反派角色张雨绮，却比主角更吸睛。</p>\r\n<p>一句“我有钱有身材，追我的人从这排到法国，你居然去泡一条鱼”让无数网友为其疯狂打call<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422413-a832ii3wh1lptajgl9icu8-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422413-a832ii3wh1lptajgl9icu8-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p><span>敢爱敢恨，敢结敢离的奇女子</span></p>\r\n<p>说她是个奇女子，倒也不失贴切。张雨绮于1986年8月8日出生于山东德州，不同于其他明星，张雨绮成长在离异家庭，一直与母亲相依为命。在母亲生意失败之际，她还一度交不出学费上学。后来，母亲无奈将结婚时购置的首饰变卖，才帮她筹齐了学费<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422415-mgmgi68w4n7zhk4xau6871-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422415-mgmgi68w4n7zhk4xau6871-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>对此，她心怀愧疚，却无能为力。个中心酸，应该也只有当事人才会懂得。这样的环境也让张雨绮迅速成长。</p>\r\n<p>在公开报道中，你会发现，张雨绮性格十分坚韧刚强。她很独立，这既是母亲的培养结果，或许也是她内心要保护母亲的信念使然<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422423-8007i93x44chpa2874pndv-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422423-8007i93x44chpa2874pndv-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>2002年5月，18岁的张雨绮签约周星驰的星辉公司而成为“星女郎”。2008年，周星驰电影“长江7号”开播，她出演女主角袁老师，一夜成名，身价暴涨<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422426-qh8gzh3ieygwvyi5ad2247-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422426-qh8gzh3ieygwvyi5ad2247-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p><span>张雨绮与袁巴元</span></p>\r\n<p>就在大家对张雨绮与王全安的离婚风波渐渐淡忘时，又有新的“炸弹”爆了出来。</p>\r\n<p>2016年10月26日，张雨绮工作室官方微博发布消息称，贝拉公主张雨绮小姐已经找到了她的野兽王子 ，两个单身的人相识十天相恋，相识七十天结婚。<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422428-d5lzeswcrhcsiqgkhtk2o4-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422428-d5lzeswcrhcsiqgkhtk2o4-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>相识70天就结了婚，没错，又是闪婚！<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422431-tonem5mxgz2imp0wr5vqzq-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422431-tonem5mxgz2imp0wr5vqzq-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>随后，该男士被爆出名为袁巴元，为上海金融界人士，是复旦大学博士、CFA，有着多年证券、基金从业经验。拥有多家公司，是个名副其实的富商。<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422432-s8kr2a35novux4gpctjxqt-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422432-s8kr2a35novux4gpctjxqt-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>但是随后又有许多关于袁巴元的负面消息被爆料出来。比如未结婚但是和前任拍了婚纱照还举办了婚礼，还留下一个女儿。并非是网上传的拥有多家公司且财力雄厚的董事长，只是时装公司的老总。还有称其因欠下巨额债务并未归还，存在两次失信纪录等等。<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422438-r15rq85mrbosbuts5rvj3m-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422438-r15rq85mrbosbuts5rvj3m-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>总之，种种信息，都显示着这个男子并非那么的清白，大家也再次为张雨绮捏了一把汗<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422440-gwk2be1sv8qtscq78k8xi4-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422440-gwk2be1sv8qtscq78k8xi4-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>然而张雨绮依然秉持原性，两耳不闻窗外事，依旧开心地过着自己的第二段婚姻生活……<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422442-baia0wvcmcpqf85raoxejn-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422442-baia0wvcmcpqf85raoxejn-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"></p>\r\n<p>其实无论是王全安还是现任袁巴元，都不是大众极力推崇的那种模范好丈夫。或许很多人都无法理解她的选择，甚至有人会觉得她眼瞎，还有人戏称她是“渣男收割机”，可张雨绮却敢去做，无畏后果。<span>在张雨绮的眼中，婚姻是一种选择，而不是一种归宿。<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422443-d96k6cnm4ql0rwwr57aqcr-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422443-d96k6cnm4ql0rwwr57aqcr-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"><br></span></p>\r\n<p>兜兜转转，希望她真的找到对的那个人。如今女神终于升级当妈，喜获一对儿女，低调炫酷地完成了人生大事，顺利加入晒娃大军，撒花祝福~<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422446-yiy2vp7zh90stnnl4gkcb4-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510928422446-yiy2vp7zh90stnnl4gkcb4-feefd78d87f5ce717db319f87ddf8e9b\"><br><a href=\"http://daily.ibaozou.com/report/6956840\">举报</a></p>\n            \n          </div>');
INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('16', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p> ▼屌丝逆袭必看<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510919012173-00coqbaxfizl9tdzb19zgo-92291abcb5df2ffaf8b1ac2bcfc2a16f!560\" class=\"shared-image\" data-width=\"550\" data-height=\"4583\" width=\"275\" height=\"2291\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510919012173-00coqbaxfizl9tdzb19zgo-92291abcb5df2ffaf8b1ac2bcfc2a16f!560\"></p>\r\n<p>▼孩子，凡事靠自己<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510919012179-gmqgkgpfyfsp341s5n6hzd-92291abcb5df2ffaf8b1ac2bcfc2a16f!560\" class=\"shared-image\" data-width=\"550\" data-height=\"5482\" width=\"275\" height=\"2741\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510919012179-gmqgkgpfyfsp341s5n6hzd-92291abcb5df2ffaf8b1ac2bcfc2a16f!560\"></p>\r\n<p>▼硬的自己受不了<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510919012182-u3fw37ztf5r7qu09g8xljj-92291abcb5df2ffaf8b1ac2bcfc2a16f!560\" class=\"shared-image\" data-width=\"550\" data-height=\"5055\" width=\"275\" height=\"2527\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510919012182-u3fw37ztf5r7qu09g8xljj-92291abcb5df2ffaf8b1ac2bcfc2a16f!560\"></p>\r\n<p> <a href=\"http://daily.ibaozou.com/report/6956834\">举报</a></p>\n            \n          </div>');
INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('17', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p>为什么你打王者荣耀排位老上不去，为什么老是遇到坑队友，王者荣耀你不知道的冷知识，有了这个还怕不能荣耀吗！<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597116-ulticr4hnt30e4a3nje5vv-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597116-ulticr4hnt30e4a3nje5vv-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\"></p>\r\n<p>1、东皇太一的球在草丛里会被看到</p>\r\n<p>2、击杀小兵最后一下(补刀)会获得额外20%左右的金钱，并且弹出来金币的颜色是深黄色</p>\r\n<p>3、队友头像框上面的绿灯表示队友有大招了，如果没绿灯就是大招在CD</p>\r\n<p>4、关羽前方有敌人的时候，马的眼睛会发光</p>\r\n<p>5、红蓝爸爸刷新时可以利用强制位移技能(鬼谷子2，钟馗钩子)勾到地形凹糟导致卡死(持续加血，不会复位)</p>\r\n<p>6、叠层数英雄(钟馗、典韦、干将)出反甲后，反弹已经死亡英雄的伤害时(如牛魔死后留下的大招地面)，反弹一次叠加一层层数<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597132-p0ffdkrm4ql3jat96yefj3-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597132-p0ffdkrm4ql3jat96yefj3-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\"></p>\r\n<p>7、芈月、太乙真人大招有前摇，可能出现技能CD人还是死了的情况</p>\r\n<p>8、花木兰重剑一技能非完全蓄力后，再次点击一技能后等待少许后会释放第二次一技能。但是完全蓄力后，需要双击一技能才能马上释放第二次。</p>\r\n<p>9、主宰的伤害是正面扇形AOE，近战吸引仇恨后可以拉着背对人群</p>\r\n<p>10、鲁班的鲨鱼炮和后羿的大招打中对方英雄后有个范围爆炸伤害，这个伤害可以打中野怪(抢主宰，抢BUFF)</p>\r\n<p>11、净化可以净化掉露娜的标记，导致断大<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597165-irwgpoy2r6b4aitj2u90cl-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597165-irwgpoy2r6b4aitj2u90cl-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\"></p>\r\n<p>12、吕布在被控瞬间开大，会造成人飞出去，不出现血阵，技能也不CD的逆天情况</p>\r\n<p>13、妲己的被动是削弱对方魔抗，这个效果队友也可以享受</p>\r\n<p>14、娜可露露经常大招飞起来跳不下去，是因为3技能位置靠近取消键，极容易拖动到取消处(这类选范围的技能都容易出现，如露娜的大招、李元芳的大招)解决办法是把2、3技能换位置<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597214-dl4wpefv9pa70ltnrnri02-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510977597214-dl4wpefv9pa70ltnrnri02-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\"></p>\r\n<p>15、芈月2技能对着空气放也能加能量条</p>\r\n<p>16、黄忠的大招有个延迟，跑得够快可以躲炮弹</p>\r\n<p>17、狄仁杰在近身处如果被动触发令牌会造成攻击不到的情况</p>\r\n<p>18、老夫子也可以R闪</p>\r\n<p>19、达摩的大招是360度判定，并不需要要在站在对面人的一侧</p>\r\n<p>20、典韦大招是所有伤害都附带真实伤害，包括火甲和反甲的伤害</p>\r\n<p>21、关于五排。五排是根据队伍中最高段位来进行匹配的。<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510978225666-5kkx7wexm15hxx8jl748lo-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510978225666-5kkx7wexm15hxx8jl748lo-99a489971c450505eb44289273a3663c\"></p>\r\n\n            \n          </div>');
INSERT INTO `article_body` VALUES ('18', '<div class=\"content\">\n            <p>在如今，韩综、日综被大量引进的风潮之下，搬运的节目并非是换一批人换一个国家就能万事大吉的，“明星大侦探”就给国内综艺做了个好榜样。节目开播三季以来，丝毫不见颓势，口碑节节升高，豆瓣评分从第一季的8.8分<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092911-5bnp5l9ibp3d8gaw53rrlc-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092911-5bnp5l9ibp3d8gaw53rrlc-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>第二季的8.9分<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092919-vmke3i0xgtn6ng0e66vnik-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092919-vmke3i0xgtn6ng0e66vnik-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>直到如今第三季逆天的9.5分<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092924-2yvft7k54yrn5cxs1acj59-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092924-2yvft7k54yrn5cxs1acj59-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>网友们不得不感叹“怎么会有综艺一直在走上！坡！路！”，真是厉害了我的明星大侦探<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092944-4hqut4g1ep0irzl503aj0p-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092944-4hqut4g1ep0irzl503aj0p-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>经过持续的口碑发酵，“明星大侦探”无论是在微博、微信还是豆瓣、知乎上都引起了很高的话题热度。#明星大侦探#微博话题截止11月13日阅读量高达53亿，讨论突破581万。长时间霸占疯狂综艺季榜单榜首，综艺话题榜第一位，成为微博热搜榜老常客。网友们纷纷参与到讨论中来，并且对“明星大侦探”给出了很高的评价，不少人表示他们是爱惨了这档节目，要强势安利，强势表白<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092948-fyv6lhfeos5300d1t724cd-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092948-fyv6lhfeos5300d1t724cd-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>这档综艺为什么会越做越“成功”呢？</p>\r\n<p><span>▼首先，是道具精良</span></p>\r\n<p>记得“明星大侦探第一季”开播时，剧组还很穷，道具寒酸，停留在棚搭场景的阶段，开播过半才有赞助商的加盟，而到了第三季已经有了花式口播和实景搭建的场景模式——制作组花了整整25天搭建出了一个真正的酒店<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092952-eoiy8qtfx2a67gb6gfsjdh-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092952-eoiy8qtfx2a67gb6gfsjdh-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>你以为这就结束了？其实更让人吃惊的还是酒店内部数不清的密道<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092956-6ooh52qfoysv2toy0fmca7-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092956-6ooh52qfoysv2toy0fmca7-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>诡异的人体实验室和“没什么卵用但依旧很走心搭出”的牢房<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092961-0tdvufih7rvo42m78h4m5l-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092961-0tdvufih7rvo42m78h4m5l-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>实景搭建拥有很强的真实感和代入感，很容易让观众产生身临其境的感觉。</p>\r\n<p><span>▼其次，是剧情烧脑</span></p>\r\n<p>酒店惊魂<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092965-h38grth5fpnwxbnp6a2b1n-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092965-h38grth5fpnwxbnp6a2b1n-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>校园欺凌<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092970-xxo8qq9wdmu8cy25rhi659-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092970-xxo8qq9wdmu8cy25rhi659-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>灵魂互换or平行时空……<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092974-p41ckr18y4fzo8xp91p0xg-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092974-p41ckr18y4fzo8xp91p0xg-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>第三季的刚开始就拥有如此多的噱头，让很多观众表示第一期就远超前两季最佳案件——“恐怖童谣”<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092978-dnh8wsot0ly7j47f0kze67-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092978-dnh8wsot0ly7j47f0kze67-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>一个“玫瑰酒店”系列就有反转反转再反转的高能剧情，能看出幕后工作人员对每一个道具细节的把控能力、每一个推理情节的策划能力，都让人叹为观止<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092982-qy036ra20dwl82y7mbmoap-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092982-qy036ra20dwl82y7mbmoap-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>在“明星大侦探”前两季大火之后，节目组没有为了圈钱故意粗制滥造，而是用心演绎每一个推理过程，把一档综艺硬是做出了刑侦电影的既视感，“明星大侦探”用收视率和高口碑给其他综艺上了一课：即使中途被停播，你爸爸依然是你爸爸<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092986-byx8sdq2adbkdaxfsdcyqg-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092986-byx8sdq2adbkdaxfsdcyqg-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p><span>▼再次，是嘉宾配合默契</span></p>\r\n<p>做真人秀，嘉宾选择很重要，“明星大侦探”的嘉宾选择又不仅仅以高学历高情商为标准，偶尔选择的蠢萌嘉宾也会为节目增添不一样的笑料。比如这一季的鬼鬼一直不理解“十四岁花季少女四年前竟然是十岁”这个新闻到底是什么意思。。。虽然鬼鬼有时蠢得可爱，是活跃气氛担当，但在第一期中，搜证能力却是一直在线的<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092990-wldi3682imzbrt9kn97ws0-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092990-wldi3682imzbrt9kn97ws0-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>白敬亭依然智商爆表，密室杀人在他面前一如既往地没难度<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092995-9fm2ubx32zw5p6ws6874gn-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092995-9fm2ubx32zw5p6ws6874gn-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>还有新加入的吴磊和张若昀，两人的口才、演技、对犯罪方法的推理能力都很让人折服<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092998-42ua5pcm8seuizmkvf2wdp-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841092998-42ua5pcm8seuizmkvf2wdp-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>撒贝宁和何老师就更不用说了，一如既往地稳定发挥，是整个团队的主心骨和领导者，几个人智商在线，配合默契，共同对案件抽丝剥茧、层层过滤，直至真相大白<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093002-xax8p301lp9c4h09ibtwui-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093002-xax8p301lp9c4h09ibtwui-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p><span>▼最后，是节目组的态度</span></p>\r\n<p>“明星大侦探”每期的节目都会聚焦社会现实，不是MC们喊个固定口号就过了，而是把想要传播的东西作为主题从始至终贯穿在剧本和人设中。比如这一期“玫瑰酒店”反映的就是校园暴力的可怕后果，在第一期中，节目组没有刻意的、硬要上升价值而上升价值，而是在一个无意的细小方面，让你感受到节目组的诚意<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093006-xh44itbkca3fiunnfxj71b-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093006-xh44itbkca3fiunnfxj71b-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>比如在“color 7”开诚布公地和撒侦探说起年轻时做的错事时，撒侦探立刻打断他们，建议“color 7”向受害者道歉，曾是校园霸凌的“color 7”用90度的鞠躬和真诚的语言，教会屏幕这边的我们如何反对校园暴力。能看出“明星大侦探”没有将单纯的娱乐大众视为最终目的，而是认真考虑过节目内涵，希望给观众带来些不一样的东西<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093010-3xuf0h21wz9xygjcol3kyr-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093010-3xuf0h21wz9xygjcol3kyr-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n<p>正是因为道具精良、故事烧脑、嘉宾默契、三观正的搭配，才成就了“明星大侦探”的高口碑，也让它做了一季又一季。不得不说真的是太惊艳了，这就是恐怖、悬疑、推理外加科幻的节奏哇，关键还非常尊重观众的智商，每一个推理都是合理而巧妙的。作为做内少有的，且制作精良的悬疑推理真人秀，婊贝们确实值得一追~<br><img src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093015-9x117ny83c9coebpci5ocb-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-src=\"https://baozouribao-qiniu.b0.upaiyun.com/ribaopic/2017/11/1510841093015-9x117ny83c9coebpci5ocb-19574338d6b254af28c312cec19b12e8\"></p>\r\n\n            \n          </div>');
